## **Abstract**

The **Aura Resonance Index (ARI)** is the resonance kernel of the **PlayNAC–EP–GERP triad**, measuring how personal aura, ecological balance, and justice harmonize to shape outcomes. ARI integrates **bio-electric signatures, socio-economic codices, non-punitive remediation (NPR), and ecological cycles** into a unified system.

Embedded within the **CARE framework (Community, Actuation, Regeneration, Equity)**, aligned with **GEO (Global Earth Overlay)**, and structured across **SOMT (Social, Economic, Political, Legal, Technical, Administrative)** dimensions, ARI provides the resonance infrastructure for a **Bio-Ecologic Economy**. Anchored in **VERTECA, SECUIR, CyberRAVE, Gunnysack, SaleBuilders, and ICARA**, ARI establishes the operational foundation for humanity’s **1,000-Year Future Map**.
